{"tid":1886603,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"第二單死亡個案係公屋石籬75歲揸拐杖廢老 大家有咩恭賀說話想講？","createTime":"2020-02-19T04:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T05:41:40.000Z","uid":242537,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"73d343c98b546eed214c50f3c7958516639b596b","tid":1886603,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:08:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chp-dashboard.geodata.gov.hk/nia/zh.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchp-dashboard.geodata.gov.hk%2Fnia%2Fzh.html&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=a557554f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chp-dashboard.geodata.gov.hk/nia/zh.html</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個廢老不值得惋惜，自己隱瞞事實，七十幾歲翻大陸搵女朋友，依家仲累到全石籬人心惶惶。好彩出事前石怡樓保安真係勤力抹lift制同大門。<br />\n<br />\n阿伯生前脾氣不嬲臭，揸住拐杖仲溫女。都係石怡樓保安同我講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3LgPhSu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LgPhSu.png&h=91880b99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"381c04767b0b05eef1ef46325c01f1a8e77dfebc","tid":1886603,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:09:50.000Z","msg":"揸住拐杖去大陸即日來回溝女係咩玩法？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1AP2jv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1AP2jv.jpg&h=2a26dba6&s={SIZE}\" />：很想要吧？"},{"pid":"70ede6720ac8130f4ac6d5c8b56e1c80851c922a","tid":1886603,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FUf08ZS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFUf08ZS.jpg&h=5094f308&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1039e5a79881de89ec7d7569eae7014ca4e26aef","tid":1886603,"uid":174060,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNbWHke.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNbWHke.png&h=be56f49a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/